text: Beatriz Nogalez González (born 3 March 1983) is a Spanish rhythmic gymnast, born in Álava. She competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Álava Category:Spanish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Basque sportspeople
